   "source": [
    "\"Assembly ward info\" contains the \"Constituency to Ward\" mapping.\n",
    "\"Booths.txt\" contains the \"Ward to Part\" mapping.\n",
    "These 2 files can be used to get the complete part/voter data of Bangalore, which can be brought into 1 array."
   ]
